Full_Description: POLYCABSUPREMA wires are manufactured using specialized Electron Beam technology. This advance technology enhances the physical, thermal and chemical properties of wire's insulation material. The molecular structure of the insulation material is cross-linked, resulting in improved heat resistance, mechanical strength and durability.
